item.title: Need Codes
item.dc:creator: @BurnInSilence BurnInSilence
item.description:
@BurnInSilence wrote:

CTRL+F find what it says right now on the tab you want to change
youll see something like

sendQuest("EMOTE", ###);

this is called a sendquest(duh :P)
change the name by changing the text in quotes, but leave the number otherwise itll send the text elsewhere
now for the case, log onto “admin” and click the tab
look at your server, it should have outprinted the case ID
now search it, and change it to do what you want
post if you have trouble with anything
